text: Anne Parillaud (b. 6 May 1960) is a French actress. She has appeared in over 30 movies since 1977. She played Nikita in the movie Nikita. She also played Marie in the horror movie Innocent Blood. Parillaud was born in Paris, France. ==References== Category:French television actors Category:French movie actors Category:Actors from Paris Category:1960 births Category:Living people
